                                  "Text":  "\u003cpre\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size:12px;\"\u003eip arp inspection vlan 20\n\ninterface range Gi0/12,Gi0/24\n  ip arp inspection trust\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e",
